19:T974,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is a reasonable price for AI consulting in Qatar?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"For an SME-focused AI strategy engagement that produces a complete implementation plan, the range is $997 to $2,497 depending on team size and scope. Enterprise AI consulting from global firms starts at QAR 150,000. The price difference reflects methodology depth, deliverable specificity, and seniority — not necessarily quality."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Should I hire a local or international AI consultant?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Both can be excellent. The critical advantage of a local consultant with GCC experience is knowledge of the regulatory environment — specifically PDPPL compliance — and understanding of the cultural and commercial context of business in Qatar. An international consultant without this knowledge may recommend tools or approaches that are not compliant with Qatari data protection law."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I evaluate an AI consultant's technical credibility?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ask them to explain a specific AI concept relevant to your business — not in abstract terms, but in terms of your specific workflow. A credible consultant should be able to explain how a WhatsApp AI concierge works for your specific industry, what data it needs, and what human oversight structure it requires — without resorting to jargon."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What red flags should I watch for in AI consulting proposals?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Three red flags: tool recommendations before workflow analysis; vague deliverables ('a roadmap', 'a strategy presentation'); and pricing that scales with implementation time rather than defined deliverables. A fixed-fee engagement with specified written deliverables is a sign of a consultant who knows what they are doing."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I know if an AI consultant's methodology is genuinely structured?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ask them to describe their process step by step. A structured methodology has specific stages, each producing a specific output, each output informing the next stage. If the description is vague or varies between conversations, the methodology is not structured — it is improvised."}}]}f:[["$","$L2",null,{"id":"faq-schema","type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$19"}}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrap","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"breadcrumb","aria-label":"Breadcrumb","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"/","children":"Home"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":"true","children":" › "}],["$","a",null,{"href":"/resources/","children":"Resources"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":"true","children":" › "}],["$","span",null,{"children":"How to Choose an AI Consultant in Qatar — 7 Questions to Ask"}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"children":"How to Choose an AI Consultant in Qatar — 7 Questions to Ask"}],[["$","p","0",{"children":"The AI consulting market in Qatar in 2026 ranges from world-class to actively harmful. There are experienced practitioners who have applied structured methodologies to real business problems. There are also generalists who read about AI on LinkedIn in 2024 and positioned themselves as experts."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"These seven questions let you distinguish between them — not by testing their AI knowledge, but by testing their methodology."}]],"$L1a",["$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e"],"$L1f","$L20","$undefined","$L21","$L22"]}]]
